refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
stringlibvirt_storagepool_get_xml_desc resourcepool
Fetch an XML document describing all aspects of the storage pool. This is suitable for defining a storagepool using libvirt_storagepool_define_xml

&reftitle.parameters;





   pool



    Storagepool resource, you can get it using various functions (e.g. libvirt_storagepool_define_xml, libvirt_storagepool_lookup_by_name).
